        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued September 11 at 5:25PM MDT until September 11 at 5:45PM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 525 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 9 miles north of
Peerless, or 22 miles northwest of Scobey, moving northeast at 10
mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Trained weather spotters. This storm has a history of 1
inch hail.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Richland and Peerless.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
